  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.8.9">
<l>viṭaiyō ṭaveṉṟāyc cimentōḷ nayanta vikirtā viḷaṅku cuṭarā ḻiyeṉṉum,</l>
<l>paṭaiyō ṭucaṅkoṉ ṟuṭaiyā yeṉaniṉ ṟimaiyōr paravu miṭampain taṭattup</l>
<l>peṭaiyō ṭuceṅkā lavaṉṉam tukaippat tokaippuṇ ṭarīkat tiṭaicceṅ kaḻunīr</l>
<l>maṭaiyō ṭaniṉṟu matuvim munāṅkūr maṇimā ṭa<supplied>k</supplied>kōyil vaṇaṅkeṉ maṉaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart, worship at Maṇimāṭa Temple in Nānkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">where nectar swells the canals, continuing to run</l>
<l rend="indent">from red waterlilies midst clusters of lotuses</l>
<l>When the red-footed swan and his mate trod [on them] in the fresh pond,</l>
<l>The place where celestials worship, continuing to call,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Wonder who, conquering the bulls so they ran,</l>
<l>Desired the milkmaid’s soft arms! You who bears the conch</l>
<l rend="indent">along with the weapon called the shining, fiery discus.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
